    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Structural lower parts of motor vehicles that include the drive trains, exhaust systems, and steering, those components that make the vehicles move and that support the vehicle bodies.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
